{
  "stem": "24195.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By Leah Shifrin Averick on December 17, 1996 in Des Plaines, Illinois.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that we were-- a train-- on a train from Berlin to Zerbst, which was our--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we left Berlin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, we were, and still, everything was fairly normal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it was a regular train, a special train, that took us to Zerbst.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not yet, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not afraid because nothing seemed to be sinister and threatening at-- at-- at this-- at that-- at that very time, I mean, at the-- at the travel.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was only a short trip-- it was like maybe a three-hour trip on the train.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't know anybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we're all the same type of person, like I'm-- like myself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we went there--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you ask them, why-- why are we here?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, you're a [NON-ENGLISH], you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You are-- that's-- so everybody-- everybody-- I mean was exchanging stories from where they had been coming from, and so forth-- where they had lived before.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They all said, we are here for the same reason, because we're half-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they're sending us to this-- they're sending us to a camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We don't know anything about this camp, yet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we go, and we-- we arrived there about three hours later.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's when the seriousness-- when the real facts became-- we became aware of what's going-- what our life is going to be now, that we're going to be incarcerated.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's going to be very, very, you know, strict, and also probably dangerous.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because big trucks, army trucks, were standing ready for us, to transport us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the-- the-- the railroad only took us to Zerbst, the city of Zerbst.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
